    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149340/extras/f7ee6c1740ebfbcc0f44f9f2b4934c46.poster.avif?t=1764673683\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149340/extras/f7ee6c1740ebfbcc0f44f9f2b4934c46.webm?t=1764673683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to PixelBurg!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The age of oppression is over – reclaim your legacy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your family’s kingdom was taken from you, but now the hour of revenge has come. Build your power, lead your army, and construct a castle worthy of your ancestors' glory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Castle Building – From Village to Fortress</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources, expand your humble farmhouse into a thriving city, and construct over 20 different buildings. Assign professions to your subjects, collect taxes, and watch your castle flourish. Every wall, every tower brings you closer to your ultimate goal: dominion over the land!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battles &amp; Defense – War for the Crown</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your enemies do not rest – defend your realm against those who once overthrew your father. Or take the fight to them: storm their castles, conquer their lands, and expand your empire. Assemble a mighty army, organize your troops, and command them in epic battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration – The World Awaits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave the safety of your walls and discover a world full of dangers and mysteries. Plunder ancient treasures, defeat bandits, and uncover valuable artifacts. But beware: not everything lurking in the wilderness can be conquered by steel…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to reclaim your kingdom?</strong></p>",
